^ C.F. Gauss. Theoria combinationis observationum erroribus minimis obnoxiae. (1821/1823)
^ Mogull, Robert G. Second-Semester Applied Statistics. Kendall/Hunt Publishing Company. 2004: 59. ISBN 0-7575-1181-3. 
